track_notes: 4 parking spots next to church/graveyard. Follow first asphalt road and then a single track trail to summit. Some rock sections have steel cable to support. A well about 2/3 of the way up did not have water in July.
track_title: From church at Bula/Pufels/Bulla to summit via Schnuerlsteig trail

track_notes: Salito da Siusi con funivia, fatto giro ad anello con gli sci con qualche saliscendi. Poi sfruttato skipass per qualche discesa, vista la neve. Cima larga si possono mettere bene anche antenne lunghe.
track_title: class E winter track with SKI,  phone OK , VHF only local
